  ID: Knight2
  Name: Balbi, clerk-turned-soldier
  Icon: {fileID: 1208347981, guid: b2407ce4cf73ad348aec15ba9990f7a1, type: 3}
  Description: "He was trained to copy legal contracts, not load powder. He took
    pride in writing clean lines; now a musket ball has ripped a crooked channel
    through his cheek and lodged near the jaw hinge. He mumbles jokes, but the bleeding
    won\u2019t stop.\n\nTreatment: Irrigate the mouth with wine and tilt the head
    to keep blood from choking him. Use forceps cautiously \u2014 a slip punctures
    the artery. If removed, pack the hole with cloth. He drinks broth for weeks if
    he lives.\n\nRequires: 4 Bandages"
